gurmukhi: ਨ ਸਿੰਘ ਹੈ ਨ ਸਯਾਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਰਾੳੁ ਹੈ ਨ ਰੰਕ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Singh Hai Na Syaar Hai Na Raao Hai Na Rank Hai||
translation: He is neither a lion, nor a jackal, nor a king nor a poor.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਮਾਨ ਹੈ ਨ ਮੳੁਤ ਹੈ ਨ ਸਾਕ ਹੈ ਨ ਸੰਕ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Maan Hai Na Maout Hai Na Saak Hai Na Sank Hai||
translation: He egoless, deathless, kinless and doubtless.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਜੱਛ ਹੈ ਨ ਗੰਧ੍ਰਬ ਹੈ ਨ ਨਰੁ ਹੈ ਨ ਨਾਰ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Jachchh Hai Na Gaddhrab Hai Na Nar(u) Hai Na Naar Hain
translation: He is neither a Yaksha, nor a Gandharva, nor a man nor a woman.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਚੋਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਸਾਹੁ ਹੈ ਨ ਸਾਹ ਕੋ ਕੁਮਾਰ ਹੈ ||੮||੧੬੮||
transliteration: Na Chor Hai Na Saah(u) Hai Na Saah Ko Koumaar Hai||8||168||
translation: He is neither a thief, nor a moneylender nor a prince.8.168.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਨੇਹ ਹੈ ਨ ਗੇਹ ਹੈ ਨ ਦੇਹ ਕੋ ਬਨਾੳੁ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Neh Hai Na Geh Hai Na Deh Ko Banaao Hai||
translation: He is without attachment, without home and without the formation of the body.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਛਲ ਹੈ ਨ ਛਿੱਦ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਛਲ ਕੋ ਮਿਲਾੳੁ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Chhal Hai Na Chhiddra Hai Na Chhal Ko Milaao Hai||
translation: He is without deceit, without blemish and without the blend of deceit.

gurmukhi: ਕ ਤੰਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਮੰਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਜੰਤ੍ਰ ਕੋ ਸਰੂਪ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Tantra Hai Na Mantra Hai Na Jantra Ko Saroophai||
translation: He is neither Tantra , nor a mantra nor the form of Yantra.

gurmukhi: ਕ ਰਾਗ ਹੈ ਨ ਰੰਗ ਹੈ ਨ ਰੇਖ ਹੈ ਨ ਰੂਪ ਹੈ ||੯||੧੬੯||
transliteration: Na Raag Hai Na Ran Hai Na Rekh Hai Na Roop Hai||9||169||
translation: He is without affection, without colour, without form and without lineage. 9.169.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਜੰਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਮੰਤ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਤੰਤ੍ਰ ਕੋ ਬਨਾੳੁ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Jantra Hai Na Mantra Hai Na Tantra Ko Banaao Hai||
translation: He is neither a Yantra, nor a Mantra nor the formation of a Tantra.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਛਲ ਹੈ ਨ ਛਿੱਦ੍ਰ ਹੈ ਨ ਛਾੲਿਅਾ ਕੋ ਮਿਲਾੳੁ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Chhal Hai Na Chhiddra Hai Na Chhaadaa Ko Milaao Hai||
translation: He is without deceit, without blemish and without the blend of ignorance.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਰਾਗ ਹੈ ਨ ਰੰਗ ਹੈ ਨ ਰੂਪ ਹੈ ਨ ਰੇਖ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Raag Hai Na Ran Hai Na Roop Hai Na Rekh Hai||
translation: He is without affection, without colour, without form and without line.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਕਰਮ ਹੈ ਨ ਧਰਮ ਹੈ ਅਜਨਮ ਹੈ ਅਬੇਖ ਹੈ ||੧੦||੧੭੦||
transliteration: Na Karam Hai Na Dharam Hai Ajanam Hai Abhekh Hai||10||170||
translation: He is actionless, religionless, birthless and guiseless. 10.170.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਤਾਤ ਹੈ ਨ ਮਾਤ ਹੈ ਅਖਯਾਲ ਅਖੰਡ ਰੂਪ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Na Taat Hai Na Maat Hai Akhyaal Akhannddroop Hai||
translation: He is without father, without nother, beyond thought and Indivisible Entity.

gurmukhi: ਅਛੇਦ ਹੈ ਅਭੇਦ ਹੈ ਨ ਰੰਕ ਹੈ ਨ ਭੁਪ ਹੈ ||
transliteration: Achhed Hai Abhed Hai Na Rank Hai Na Bhoop Hai||
translation: He is Invincible and Indiscriminate; He is neither a pauper nor a king.
